        "َ°“ƒ  Audio" \
        "َ°چ¹  Display" \
        "َ°–°  Window" \
        "َ°¹‘  Screenshot" \
        "َ°¥°  Processes" \
        "َ°ڈ—  Packages" \
        "ï’µ  Applications" \
        "َ°¸‰  Wallpapers" \
